uppercase, etc.), of that string. The script will also tell us the stringâ€™s first and last words, when they are sorted alphabetically. Weâ€™ll need to utilize numerous methods on the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">str</code> class and some of the functions used to sort lists to make all of this this happen. Hereâ€™s how we want the script to be used:</p>

