</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Separate the String and Present the Individual Words as a List
For the remaining requirements of our script, we need to work with the individual words. Because of this, weâ€™re going to store the words off as a new variable, words. We can get the words by using the str.split method. After weâ€™ve separated the message into words, letâ€™s also print them out:</p>

<p>~/variations.py</p>

<p>#!/usr/bin/env python3.7</p>

<p>message = input(â€œEnter a message: â€œ)</p>

<p>print(â€œLowercase:â€, message.lower())
